Hi folks! This is feedback for HubSpot. You have this great documentation of making themes. There is file called fields.json and its documentation (<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/themes#fields-json>). I think your example is missing brackets `[…]` and it is not working right now. Should it be like this maybe?

```[{
   "type": "group",
   "name": "typography",
   "label": "Typography",
   "children": [
     {
       "type": "font",
       "name": "h1_font",
       "label": "Heading 1",
       "load_external_fonts": true,
       "default": {
         "color": "#000",
         "font": "Merriweather",
         "font_set": "GOOGLE",
         "variant": "700",
         "size": "48"
       }
     }
  ]
}]```
There were feedback bubble earlier but I can’t see it right now, so I’ll post this here.
